data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT LTM_Lease.LeaseID ,LTM_Lease.LeaseName ,LTM_Lease.LeaseShortName ,LTM_Lease.LeaseAgreementIDFormated ,LTM_Lease.CompanyID , LTM_Lease.LeaseAgreementIDFormated + ' ' + LTM_Lease.LeaseShortName AS LeaseNumberAndName FROM LTM_Lease ORDER BY LeaseAgreementIDFormated ASC
